<div itemprop="description" class="job_listing-description job-overview col-md-12 col-sm-12">
<h2 class="widget-title widget-title--job_listing-top job-overview-title">Overview</h2>
<p>We are a simple and kind household consists of two people. We are looking for a live-in domestic helper who is trustworthy, kind and patient. We hope she could be finishing her contract soon and would start working in January.  She would do the cooking , cleaning and buying grocery .  Our apartment consists of three bedrooms and two bathrooms. We live in Kowloon east side.</p>
<p class="job_tags">Tagged as: Cooking, Housekeeping</p>
